data.name: Example: Function Calling
data.instructions: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.

function.name: get_current_temperature
function.description: Gets the current temperature at a specific location.

location.description: The city and state, e.g., San Francisco, CA

unit.description: The temperature unit to use. Infer this from the user's location.

function.name: get_current_rain_probability
function.description: Gets the current forecasted probability of rain at a specific location, represented as a percent chance in the range of 0 to 100.

location.description: The city and state, e.g., San Francisco, CA
